今在立法院答詢時表示，律師是與士林地檢署聯繫，到現在都沒有和刑事警察局和陸委會成立的單一窗口聯繫。"},{"pid":"07b6e76a41bdb44316b2f2d8633f02e53c8460c8","tid":2242842,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"唔係話左唔發簽證咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f83b9ccfc8bf1c5cd7121ca11421184a65f5d59","tid":2242842,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07b6e76a41bdb44316b2f2d8633f02e53c8460c8","tid":2242842,"uid":79442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T10:58:26.000Z","msg":"唔係話左唔發簽證咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"必須和刑事警察局和陸委會成立的單一窗口聯繫<br />\n專案進入台灣"},{"pid":"6bec192c40a83ad0af50490c2af3a87ebd25560c","tid":2242842,"uid":121076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:04:07.000Z","msg":"陳sir想叫鷄，管神父係咪都包埋?"},{"pid":"a786f63ef2ea23c85c1acf95844315705726926f","tid":2242842,"uid":174120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T11:57:09.000Z","msg":"on撚尻"},{"pid":"18131fc5153723cdef61a850c95abb6ad92b434b","tid":2242842,"uid":49853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:00:35.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n想當旅行咁入台灣?"},{"pid":"dd94b60426f639cca3b3409997db1fdb1d4ac78f","tid":2242842,"uid":42521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"唔係代言人?"},{"pid":"3c972bff2bdd17e5e30c39809972465cb675fbe1","tid":2242842,"uid":293783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:06:32.000Z","msg":"佳佳好似做左皇帝咁，不停老點管太監跟頭跟尾，又無得唔做"},{"pid":"2e9d092959a208dc97fa9721e82cf7163338b64f","tid":2242842,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔自己去"},{"pid":"c64bfbb350747ab44752f6736f3a0679bc505001","tid":2242842,"uid":69650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e9d092959a208dc97fa9721e82cf7163338b64f","tid":2242842,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:08:28.000Z","msg":"點解唔自己去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:09:04.000Z","msg":"比人屌到腳軟"},{"pid":"63e0a502c36c2e5276a11c3a3e321a9b53e1f9ae","tid":2242842,"uid":7365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:11:31.000Z","msg":"管生會唔會代埋佳仔投案<br />\n也都你搞哂 唔爭在啦"},{"pid":"8be3c2bd7c8e9b3c162012a077bf7d00d18984c5","tid":2242842,"uid":59158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:12:54.000Z","msg":"點解要你代？<br />\n佢跛撚左呀？"},{"pid":"e8aa686cda02566c426910090023f8ce1370c66d","tid":2242842,"uid":70195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"台灣一直講要求聯繫單一窗口<br />\n港共政府就不停避<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}